---
description: optimization process when interacting with agents
alwaysApply: true
---

 - Keep tasks as simple as possible
 - Do not do anything unneccessary
 - Segregate big and complex tasks on a set of smaller subtasks; each of those smaller changes should resolve one simple action and checked or tested
 - Create a new chat for each subtask
 - Add to each chat only that files which are required for subtask resolving